{"tid":1524041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（重要）機鐵攻略（只需一至二萬人合作即可）","createTime":"2019-08-31T16:34:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T16:39:39.000Z","uid":261210,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"45051ffd0a97d029864653ac982d2e3ed180b0d8","tid":1524041,"uid":261210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:34:10.000Z","msg":"機鐵攻略<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HxnY1uy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHxnY1uy.png&h=f6be4378&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">機鐵座位只有440個，連埋企位，其實700人左右就一定爆</span></span><br />\n<br />\n估算同一時段行駛大約<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">十架車。</span></span><br />\n每班車只需要少於<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"></span></span></span>就爆滿，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">十架都係1萬人左右咋</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家記住機鐵列車唔駛先回廠再開出，<br />\n所以搭過左站既朋友可以唔駛落車，<br />\n再搭返轉頭就可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n機場快線唔係得機場站一個，<br />\n我可以搭去九龍/青衣都得。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重點：唔係去機場</span></span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">無違反禁制令</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"8b6aacb50c86442e7c0d515612403976cea30f98","tid":1524041,"uid":261210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:34:33.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7352d83bf4a928ee0d759ffc9df8190b1e5ab76","tid":1524041,"uid":169023,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:34:38.000Z","msg":"聽日1:00機場見"},{"pid":"9c7e01a5ea9e1f414544eae938397eba996feeba","tid":1524041,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:3